name: The Courtship
description: "The Courtship" is an abstract composition of two courting roses. The artwork explores a unique use of abstract shapes and color to depict the act of two roses falling in love. This work was created by Kvasir Vanir during a time in his life when he felt lonely and disconnected from the joys in life. Resolution: 9180 x 9180, Format: PNG. @KvasirArt
